                                                                                  <h4>Sustaining the Celtic Seas</h4>
                                        <div class="description-container">
                      We've been instrumental in setting up the Celtic Seas Partnership, an ambitious project which aims to find new ways of managing the marine environment.
                                                                      <div class="find-out-more-container">
                          <a href="">
                                                          Find out more
                                                        <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i>
