                                                                                  <h4>Improving Scottish fisheries</h4>
                                        <div class="description-container">
                      We were involved in the Common Fisheries Policy reform process and are now engaged in its implementation.
                                                                      <div class="find-out-more-container">
                          <a href="">
                                                          Find out more
                                                        <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i>
                          </a>
                        </div>
